Area of Effect  : Room
Aggressive      : Yes
Accumulative    : No
Duration        : Proficiency
Classes         : Monk           Level 60
===============================================
 
One of the monk's most devious chants, the sonata of malaise
invokes such a sense of anger and fear that it hampers the
monk's opponents movements such that they are less likely to
dodge certain spell effects.  This chant hurts all of the
victims' saves.
 
