"SOUL TAP"

================================================
Usage         : cast 'soul tap' <victim>
Aggressive    : Yes
Type of spell : Sphere of Generic
Classes       : Necromancer
================================================
 
Like an advanced form of energy drain, this spell allows a
necromancer to leech energy from a living victim's very soul,
causing the victim significant anguish.  However, tapping
a soul has a prolonged enrichening effect, increasing the
user's ability to regenerate his or her own life energies for
some time.
 
See Also: ENERGY DRAIN, NECROMANCER
